# Design System

## Theme
- Dark theme ONLY. No light mode. All colors via HSL CSS variables in `src/index.css`.
- Primary/Gold: `hsl(43 96% 46%)` — CTAs, active states, accents, ratings
- Background: `hsl(222 30% 7%)` — deep navy
- Card: `hsl(222 25% 11%)` — panels, elevated surfaces
- Muted: `hsl(222 20% 15%)` — disabled states, borders
- Destructive: `hsl(0 72% 51%)` — errors, losses, injuries

## Glass Morphism Pattern
Use the `<GlassPanel>` component for all card-like containers:
```tsx
<GlassPanel className="p-4">content</GlassPanel>
```
Underlying classes: `bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-border/50 rounded-xl`

## Typography
- Headings: `font-display` class (Oswald font)
- Body: default sans (DM Sans)
- Tiny labels: `text-[10px] text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider`
- Stat numbers: `font-mono font-black`

## Rating Colors (used everywhere)
```
≥80 → text-emerald-400
≥70 → text-primary (gold)
≥60 → text-amber-400
<60 → text-muted-foreground
```

## Layout
- Mobile-first: `max-w-lg mx-auto px-4`
- Top bar: `h-14`, fixed, blur background
- Bottom nav: `h-16`, fixed, 5 tabs
- Content area: `pt-14 pb-20` (clears top/bottom bars)
- Safe area: `safe-area-bottom` utility class

## Spacing
- Page sections: `space-y-4`
- Inside panels: `p-4` standard, `p-3` compact, `p-5` hero sections
- Grid gaps: `gap-3` for cards, `gap-2` for compact lists

## Animations
- Page transitions: Framer Motion `opacity + y` (see GameShell.tsx)
- Match events: `AnimatePresence` with slide-in
- Buttons: `active:scale-[0.98]` on interactive panels

## Don'ts
- Don't use raw hex colors — always use CSS variables or Tailwind color classes
- Don't use `px-*` values larger than `px-6` on mobile
- Don't add shadows beyond `shadow-lg` — the glass effect handles depth
- Don't use `dark:` prefix — we're always dark mode
